SELECT <%=sourceSystem%>  || 'ProductionOrder_' || "AFKO"."MANDT" || '_' || "AFKO"."AUFNR" AS "ID",
       CAST("AUFK"."ERDAT" AS DATE) + CAST("AUFK"."ERFZEIT" AS TIME)                       AS "CreationTime",
	<%=sourceSystem%>  || 'User_' || "AUFK"."MANDT" || "AUFK"."ERNAM"                         AS "CreatedBy",
       CASE
           WHEN "USR02"."USTYP" IN ('B', 'C') THEN 'Automatic'
           ELSE 'Manual' END                                                               AS "CreationExecutionType",
       CAST("AFKO"."GSTRS" AS DATE) + CAST("AFKO"."GSUZS" AS TIME)                         AS "ScheduledStartTime",
       CAST("AFKO"."GLTRS" AS DATE) + CAST("AFKO"."GLUZS" AS TIME)                         AS "ScheduledFinishTime",
       CAST("AFKO"."GSTRI" AS DATE) + CAST("AFKO"."GSUZI" AS TIME)                         AS "StartTime",
       CAST("AFKO"."GLTRI" AS DATE) + CAST("AFKO"."GEUZI" AS TIME)                         AS "FinishTime",
       'SAP'                                                                               AS "SourceSystemType",
       "AFKO"."MANDT"                                                                      AS "SourceSystemInstance",
       CAST("AFKO"."AUFNR" AS VARCHAR(255))                                                AS "SystemProductionOrderNumber",
       CAST("AFKO"."AUFNR" AS VARCHAR(255))                                                AS "DatabaseProductionOrderNumber"
FROM "AFKO" AS "AFKO"
         LEFT JOIN "AUFK" AS "AUFK"
                   ON "AFKO"."MANDT" = "AUFK"."MANDT"
                       AND "AFKO"."AUFNR" = "AUFK"."AUFNR"
         LEFT JOIN "USR02" AS "USR02"
                   ON "AUFK"."MANDT" = "USR02"."MANDT"
                       AND "AUFK"."ERNAM" = "USR02"."BNAME"
WHERE "AUFK"."MANDT" IS NOT NULL
  AND "AUFK"."AUTYP" IN ('10')
